# Feature navigation

- `:integration:navigation` / `IdeNavHost` only wires **cross-feature** exits (inject `*Screens`, call `NavHost(...)`).
- Each feature owns list‚Üîcreate (and similar) **sub-navigation** inside its `*Screens` / `*NavHost`.
- Do not put feature toasts, dialogs, or screen state in `IdeNavHost`.

```kotlin
// ‚ùå BAD ‚Äî IdeNavHost shows projects toast / owns create route
// ‚úÖ GOOD
projectsScreens.NavHost(onOpenProject = { id -> /* cross-feature only */ })
```
